Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.44,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,請放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,我會先與他們會合的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.12,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,把路讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:48.88,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,范大人
