Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:01.77,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,要小心喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:08.54,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:14.64,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,我們一定會再次相遇的
